{
  "stem": "21812.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there Sugihara, the Japanese consul-- her father had, as being one of the-- since he had been in the Polish government, he-- Roosevelt had issued visas to-- to intellectuals, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a certain number of visas.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he had one of those.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But he didn't have a-- a visa to-- you needed a transit visa.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Even if you had a visa to the United States, you had to have a transit visa to cross Russia to get into Japan to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And Sugihara provided that transit visa for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So excuse me, so what I wanted to say was--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--that-- that-- so we had such similar experiences, her having that-- having to go through Siberia to come here, so, you know, we talk about that constantly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's very helpful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a very good thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think-- I think once or twice I might have had a dream that had some connection with that, yeah.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe once or twice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't recall any particular.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went back in-- first time in '69.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I went back again-- Sylvia hadn't seen Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went after we went to Warsaw and we went to Auschwitz and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We went to Vienna about six years ago.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think at that point I had worked out most of my hatred and-- for the Austrians and for the-- that things that I-- you know, my own experiences.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wanted to see-- have my first wife see Vienna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have a-- also have a cousin in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I went back for--",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
